    <div id="rec-ebook-section" class="block5 subject_show">
    

    
  

  <h2>
    <span>喜欢读&#34;西班牙旅行笔记&#34;的人也喜欢的电子书</span>
      &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;

  </h2>


    <div class="tips-mod">
        支持 Web、iPhone、iPad、Android 阅读器
    </div>
    <div class="content clearfix">
        
        <dl>
            <dt>
            <a href="https://read.douban.com/ebook/32936725/?dcs=subject-rec&amp;dcm=douban&amp;dct=1962923" target="_blank">
                <span class="cover-outer">
                <img src="https://pic.arkread.com/cover/ebook/f/32936725.1653705783.jpg!cover_default.jpg">
                </span>
            </a>
            </dt>
